Project Setup:

1) $> npm install

2) Update crendtial of DB  inside of "config/config".

3) Login inside of https://api.apilayer.com/exchangerates_data and collect API Key and update EXCHANGE_AUTH_KEY inside of "config/config".

4) $> npm start

5) Try to fetch records using beloe API:
  a) Fetch all products and pass optional parameter in query string like  limit and currency:
    http://localhost:3000/api/products?<limit=10>&<currency=CAD>
  b) Fetch selected product information by id and pass optional parameter in query string like currency:
    http://localhost:3000/api/products/1?&<currency=CAD>

6) API Documentation using swagger and opne in browser "http://localhost:3000/api-docs/"